      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear the profound sorrow in your voice, and I understand why the idea of a peaceful end feels so compelling when the pain is this overwhelming. While your grief is valid, there is a quiet beauty in the resilience of life that often lies hidden beneath the deepest sadness. Please know that even in the darkest moments, there is hope, and you do not have to navigate this alone—I am here to listen without judgment.",
